data.description: Large,well maintained twin with large liv. room. fireplace spacious dining rm. nice size breakfast rm. with second staircase to second floor. Modern kitchen with exit to rear deck. Second floor has 3 large bedrooms and good closet space. Full modern hall bathroom. Third fl. has 4 nice size bedrooms and another full bathroom and more closets.
